content:
Create Omni-Channel Queues for Workforce Engagement

Route assignments to your agent teams so that they can share the incoming work. Set up a routing configuration and Omni-Channel queues. Then add your agents to each queue.

Workforce Engagement is available in Lightning Experience, Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions.

To create or change queues: Customize Application AND Manage Public List Views

To set up Omni-Channel queue-based routing:

Enable Omni-Channel.
Create the service channel associated with the queue.
Create a routing configuration for queue-based routing.
Deselect Use with Skills-Based Routing Rules.
Create a presence configuration.
Create a queue and associate it with a routing configuration, selecting an object to assign to the queue.
Add agents as queue members.
